## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

Azure Service Broker has the following requirements:

+ PCF version v1.8 or later

+ [Azure Subscription](https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/pricing/purchase-options/) and [service principal](https://github.com/cloudfoundry-incubator/bosh-azure-cpi-release/blob/master/docs/get-started/create-service-principal.md)

